%details
  %summary How we use cookies
  %p We use cookies for security, functionality, and analytics purposes.
  %ul
    %li
      We use the
      %code _ulab_website_session
      cookie to track sessions.
    %li
      Cloudflare sets the
      = link_to 'https://support.cloudflare.com/hc/en-us/articles/200170156-What-does-the-CloudFlare-cfduid-cookie-do' do
        %code _cfduid
      cookie to identify trusted web traffic.
    %li
      Google Analytics sets the
      = link_to 'https://developers.google.com/analytics/devguides/collection/analyticsjs/cookie-usage' do
        = succeed ',' do
          %code _ga
        = succeed ', and' do
          %code _gat
        %code _gid
      cookies for analytics purposes. We do not use Google Analytics Advertising features.
